sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant API as Auth Controller
    participant SVC as Auth Service
    participant DB as Database (Prisma)
    participant JWT as JWT Strategy
    participant G as Google OAuth

    Note over C,G: Register Local
    C->>API: POST /auth/register {email, password, fullName}
    API->>SVC: register(dto)
    SVC->>DB: check email uniqueness
    SVC->>SVC: hash password (bcrypt)
    SVC->>DB: create User + RefreshToken
    SVC-->>C: {accessToken, refreshToken}

    Note over C,G: Login Local
    C->>API: POST /auth/login {email, password}
    API->>SVC: loginWithLocal(dto)
    SVC->>DB: find User by email
    SVC->>SVC: verify password
    SVC->>DB: check isActive
    SVC->>DB: store RefreshToken (hashed)
    SVC-->>C: {accessToken, refreshToken, user}

    Note over C,G: Login Google
    C->>API: GET /auth/google
    API->>G: redirect to Google consent
    G-->>API: callback with code
    API->>G: exchange code to profile
    G-->>API: {email, name, googleSub}
    API->>SVC: handleGoogleLogin(profile)
    SVC->>DB: find AuthProviderRecord(GOOGLE, googleSub)
    alt user exists
        SVC->>DB: check isActive
    else user not found
        SVC->>DB: create User + AuthProviderRecord
    end
    SVC-->>C: {accessToken, refreshToken, user}

    Note over C,G: Refresh Token
    C->>API: POST /auth/refresh {refreshToken}
    API->>SVC: refreshTokens(dto)
    SVC->>DB: find RefreshToken by hash
    SVC->>SVC: check expired and not revoked
    SVC->>DB: revoke old token
    SVC->>DB: create new RefreshToken
    SVC-->>C: {accessToken, refreshToken}

    Note over C,G: Authenticated Request
    C->>API: GET /bookings (Header: Bearer accessToken)
    API->>JWT: validate token
    JWT->>DB: load user by sub
    JWT->>DB: check isActive
    JWT->>DB: match tenantId claim vs DB
    JWT->>DB: check tenant isActive
    JWT-->>API: CurrentUserPayload
    API-->>C: bookings data
